msgid "problem_p1"
msgstr "Page Rules and Cache Rules are powerful, but mistakes can hit checkout, APIs, and the admin in one shot."

msgid "problem_p2"
msgstr "Without a fast path back to the last working state, people avoid touching Cloudflare during an outage—and slow rollback stacks revenue and trust damage."

msgid "problem_p3"
msgstr "What matters is stable behavior and a way to return to the last working state—not another dashboard that only talks about speed."

